<LP>
   SUNNYVALE, Calif. -- Telebit Corp. said it offered
2,090,000 common shares for $20.9 million, or $10 a share, in
an initial public offering.
   The maker of data-transmission products said that of the
shares being offered, 1,928,820 are being sold by Telebit and
