Revco would sell all its stores in Illinois, Iowa, Indiana,
Kansas, Kentucky, Michigan, Missouri and western Tennessee.
   Acadia Partners is a Fort Worth, Texas-based partnership
that includes Robert M. Bass. Last year a group led by the
Texas billionaire made an unsuccessful $925 million offer for
all of Revco.
   Reliable Drug Stores is a drugstore chain based in
Indianapolis.
